* CSV Export: Exports race results to a CSV file.
*   When to use:    After the race to export results for external use.
*   How to use:     Double-click to generate the CSV file in the race folder.
*   Output:         Creates a file named ~Results.csv in the race folder.
*   Note:           The ~ prefix places the file in the race directory.
Output Format       CSV
Destination         ~Results.csv
No Page Numbers
Records Per Page    100000
List DNF
Dq Field            DNF

Select              BIB
>                   0
Field               BIB
Field               Name
Field               Sex
Field               AGE
Field               DIV
Field               City
Field               State
Field               DIVPLACE
Field               DIVTOTAL
Field               SEXPLACE
Field               SEXTOTAL
Field               PACE

Event               Finish
minus               GunStart
Time Format         H:MM:SS.01
Field Header        Gun Time

Event               Finish
minus               ChipStart
Time Format         H:MM:SS.01
Field Header        Chip Time